&lt;h2 id=&quot;duplicating-a-method&quot;&gt;Duplicating a Method&lt;&#x2F;h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Letâ€™s take the &lt;code&gt;SanitizeCrypto()&lt;&#x2F;code&gt; function
